Text: but she is very good looking..do we know her?

Ugh!  This again!  

Check the screenshots before you download this.  I've downloaded this maybe a dozen times, under a dozen different names, over a period of years.  So I guess it must be popular.

"You're an obediant little fucktoy, aren't you?"

"Tee-hee!"

Sure, it's offensive and degrading, but it's also pretty vacant and dull.  .  The off-camera male voice drones on idiotically.  The  woman is a little too convincing in acting retarded (her eyes are scary!) the man can just barely get it up, and the camera work is awful.   How does he manage to fuck her in the ass for an extended close-up. and still not give us a good idea of what her ass looks like?

P, you've uploaded some fine stuff, and for that, I thank you.
